</code></pre> What are the system requirements for running agent-orchestra? <p>The system requirements for agent-orchestra include:</p> <ul> <li>Operating System: Linux, macOS, or Windows</li> <li>Docker: Version 20.10 or higher</li> <li>Memory: At least 4GB of RAM</li> <li>CPU: At least 2 CPU cores</li> </ul> <p>Ensure your system meets these requirements for optimal performance.</p> How do I upgrade agent-orchestra to the latest version? <p>To upgrade agent-orchestra, follow these steps:</p> <ol> <li>Pull the Latest Image: Pull the latest Docker image:    ```bash docker pull agent-orchestra/agent-orchestra:latest <pre><code>2. **Stop the Current Container**: Stop and remove the current container:
